  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0dd9\u0daf\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0db4\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dda \u0d9c\u0dd9\u0dbd \u0d9a\u0db4\u0dcf \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dbd\u0dcf \u0d9c\u0d9f\u0da7 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Father of two cuts neck and throws Nilwala into river",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Akuressa Police have killed a father and seriously injured a mother and daughter by stabbing them with a sharp object at a house in the Thibbatuwa area in Akuressa.",
        "Police say a 69-year-old father was brutally beheaded in the living room, his head thrown into the Nilwala River and his wife and daughter beaten with a sharp object.",
        "The victim was identified as Wellara Tantirige Sumanapala (69), a resident of Kalugamahena, Walakadawatta, Thalagassa, Thalagassa, Akuressa.",
        "Police suspect Kida has been killed in a long-running dispute. A senior police officer said that the blood marks showed that the head had been cut with a sword and thrown into the Nilwala river.",
        "Several police teams have launched a search operation in the area to find the 29-year-old killer, who is accused of harassing police in a number of cases of various crimes and assaults on women in the area."
      ],
